::Striker::

"I got him," Striker says to Shadow Wing, walking forward and picking up 
Rhinox, setting off toward the CR chambers. Having taken a few steps, the 
panel above Striker's head detatches from the cealing, Striker barely jumping 
back in time as the panel smashes into the floor. He breathes out a sigh of 
relief, looking at Rhinox to make sure the bot wasn't hit by the panel.

"Be careful. This place is falling apart," Striker says, walking off again 
toward the CR chamber, another panel smashing into the floor behind him.
